videos.headline: Bulldogs put 7 on the board in less than 90 seconds
videos.description: D'Andre Swift rushes up the middle for a 3-yard touchdown to put Georgia on the board first vs. Murray State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bulldogs put 7 on the board in less than 90 seconds) 2019/9/7

videos.headline: Murray State's Green takes off for 60-yard TD
videos.description: Murray State QB Preston Rice finds former Florida Gator Daquon Green and he takes off running for the end zone, surprising Georgia with a 60-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Murray State's Green takes off for 60-yard TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Murray State forces early turnover vs. Georgia
videos.description: Jake Fromm connects with Eli Wolf for 8 yards, but Wolf is quickly sacked by Murray State defense forcing the ball to pop out of his hands.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Murray State forces early turnover vs. Georgia) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Herrien punches it in for Georgia TD
videos.description: Brian Herrien pushes his way through Murray State's defense for a 2-yard touchdown for Georgia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Herrien punches it in for Georgia TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Reed completes Georgia's scoop-and-score
videos.description: The Bulldogs force Murray State's Jared McCray to lose control of the ball and J.R. Reed is there to pick it up and return the ball 14 yards for touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia's Pickens dives for impressive catch
videos.description: George Pickens shows impressive vision as he dives to haul in a pass from Jake Fromm, gaining 43 yards on a touchdown drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia's Pickens dives for impressive catch) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Blaylock's TD adds to Georgia's dominant lead
videos.description: Dominick Blaylock punches his first collegiate touchdown with a 25-yard rushing strike to add to Georgia's lead vs. Murray State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blaylock's TD adds to Georgia's dominant lead) 2019/9/7

videos.headline: Georgia makes easy work of Murray State in blowout win
videos.description: Stetson Bennett throws for two touchdowns and rushes for another to power Georgia to a 63-17 win against Murray State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Georgia makes easy work of Murray State in blowout win) 2019/9/7 ESHEET SOTFULL
